track_notes: You must Park in the village Sauze then you will found a nice path in the forest, this is not long nor difficult, in summer take some water. Plenty room for antennas, on the way back you can visit the table dorientation on top of the village.
I did not use snowshoes but on some place the ground is icy and you must walk carefully.
track_title: same as 2 years ago but in wintertime

track_notes: Start from the village Sauze (parking) we did this path clockwise; it is not difficult, but about 10 km. Plenty room on summit (GSM ok)
